channel.title: What a day ive had
channel.description:
ok the bad luck started when i came out of my local sports + social club my mother and sister went out before me and they had something of mine on them so i started running out side just before i got to the door out i tripped and did a full front role narrowly missing the door that was embarasing everyone stoped and there was silence lol i got up and said "im ok!" and walked out
then when i got home i was watching a video on how to make a stun gun out of a camera, now my friend is pro at making them so i tried considering they can go up to 7000 volts fully charged you have to be carefull first i got a shock when i touched the transformer thing (the thing that charges it up) it was that bad then later on i touched the 2 wires that you use to give the shock and as you guessed it i got another
this time there was a massive spark my cousen said i screamed really load and i fell backwards on my chair that hurt but i was ok
oh btw the shock didnt make me fly back it was just me totally shitting myself (not literly) and jumping backwards
what a day huh?
